1. Class User
-------------
    - userID: int
    - userName: String
    - email: String
    - password: String
    - phone: String
    - role: String  // "user" or "admin"

2. Class Movie
--------------
    - movieID: int
    - title: String
    - genre: String
    - language: String
    - duration: String
    - description: String

3. Class Theatre
----------------
    - theatreID: int
    - name: String
    - location: String
    - halls: List<Hall>

4. Class Hall
-------------
    - hallID: int
    - name: String
    - seatLayout: SeatLayout

5. Class SeatLayout
-------------------
    - rows: int
    - columns: int
    - seats: List<Seat>

6. Class Seat
-------------
    - seatID: String
    - row: int
    - column: int
    - isAvailable: boolean
    - category: String  // e.g., Regular, VIP

7. Class Show
-------------
    - showID: int
    - movie: Movie
    - hall: Hall
    - showTime: String
    - availableSeats: List<Seat>

8. Class Booking
----------------
    - bookingID: int
    - user: User
    - show: Show
    - bookedSeats: List<Seat>
    - bookingTime: String
    - totalAmount: double
    - paymentStatus: String
    - isCancelled: boolean

9. Class Payment
----------------
    - paymentID: int
    - booking: Booking
    - amountPaid: double
    - paymentMethod: String  // UPI, Card, etc.
    - paymentStatus: String  // Success/Failed

10. Class CancellationPolicy
----------------------------
    - booking: Booking
    - refundAmount: double
    - cancelledAt: String
    - isRefunded: boolean

11. Class Notification
----------------------
    - user: User
    - message: String
    - method: String  // Email/SMS
    - sentAt: String

12. Class AdminPanel
--------------------
    - movies: List<Movie>
    - shows: List<Show>
    - theatres: List<Theatre>
    - addMovie(), removeMovie()
    - addShowtime(), manageSeats()

13. Class Dashboard
-------------------
    - theatre: Theatre
    - totalBookings: int
    - totalRevenue: double
    - topMovies: List<Movie>
    - occupancyRate: double


Feature	                                        Classes Involved
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Register & Login	                              User
Browse movies & showtimes	                      Movie, Show
Theatre selection with seat layout            	Theatre, Hall, SeatLayout, Seat
Live seat availability                        	Seat, Show
Book tickets (single/multiple)	                Booking, Seat, Show, User
Filter by location, language, genre           	Movie, Theatre
Payment gateway integration (mock)	            Payment, Booking
Ticket history and download	                    Booking, User
Cancellation with refund policy	Cancellation    Policy, Booking
Notification via email/SMS (mock)	              Notification, User
Admin panel to add/remove movies              	AdminPanel, Movie
Showtime and seat management	                  Show, Hall, AdminPanel
Dashboard for theatre analytics               	Dashboard, Theatre, Booking, Show
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

